(182, 1, 'Star Wars Are Ewoks Scared of Stormtroopers?', 2, 'Meet the Ewoks of Endor', 'Get little Star Wars fans reading with this DK Reader, Star Wars Are Ewoks Scared of Stormtroopers?\r\n\r\nIn Star Wars Are Ewoks Scared of Stormtroopers? you''ll meet the Ewoks that live on the forest moon of Endor. They may be small, but they have a lot to fight for. Featuring battles and match-ups across the galaxy like Yoda vs Dooku, Anakin vs droid control ship, and Ewoks vs Stormtroopers, this reader shows you that sometimes, size matters not!\r\n\r\nDK Readers are great for children who are beginning to read. The exciting stories with limited vocabulary and lots of word repetition engage young fans and build their literary skills. The winning combination of popular subject Star Wars and an engaging story packed full of exciting images is perfect for getting children hooked on reading. This eBook also includes read-along audio which highlights the words as it reads them and is carefully paced for the specific Reader level.', 'Catherine Saunders', 'star_wars_are_ewoks_scared_of_stormtroopers_1.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 'star_wars_are_ewoks_scared_of_stormtroopers_1.epub', 'star_wars_are_ewoks_scared_of_stormtroopers_sample_1.epub', '2014-08-29', '9780241012109', '9780241012093', '|Star Wars|', 'PUBLISHED', '2014-08-18 11:28:10', '2014-09-26 15:26:36'),
